Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn@華康海報體W12\frz269.789\bord3\shad0\fs50\3a&H01&\3c&H977A1A&\pos(1221,344)}記不住動畫角色神馬的
